Hey all im back from a long break from hammer, and as always im giving you guys a nice crack at my beta version. This is aim_vm_texture_b1 which stands for aim VermillioN (my gaming name) texture beta1. Any bugs or technical glitchs you find please send me a pm so that i may fix it up for beta 2. and if you have any ideas or improvements make a post. if you put this on your server please pm me i would love to stop by.
